Logs
-----
- log output to log file
- log output to syslog


ACL
----
- one acl file for each service
- log of acl file changes
- threadsafe acl list switch


AUTHENTICATION
----
- split authentication according to @<inst> suffix
- LDAP support
- AD support
- OAUTH2 support


Dockerization
-----------
- list of all env variables
- dockerized version of DAS
- compose file docker registry+DAS


